%% Diagram: OT variant decision tree
%% Type: flowchart
%%{init: {'htmlLabels': false}}%%
flowchart TD
    A["Need real-time collaborative editing"] --> B{"Can mandate central server\nand acceptable RTT?"}
    B -->|Yes| C["Client-server OT\n(Jupiter / Wave model)"]
    C --> C1["TP1 only; ACK rule;\nGoogle Docs, Office 365,\nCKEditor 5, ShareDB, ot.js"]

    B -->|No — offline-first or P2P| D{"Strict OT semantics required?\n(per-op intent, op log auditable)"}
    D -->|No — eventual convergence is enough| E["Use a CRDT\n(Yjs, Automerge, RGA)"]
    D -->|Yes — must be OT| F{"Topology"}
    F -->|"Mostly central with\nrare offline windows"| C
    F -->|"True P2P / federated"| G["Extended-signature OT\n(TTF or COT)"]
    G --> G1["TP2 satisfied via tombstones\nor context vectors;\nlimited production exposure"]
